Installation Requirements :

Instructions on how to set up postgres can be found here 

http://www-unix.globus.org/ogsa/docs/alpha3/services/reliable_transfer.html

download http://www.mcs.anl.gov/~madduri/multifile_rft.tar.gz

tar -xvzf multifile_rft.tar.gz

cd multirft

edit <service > section of MultiFileRFTFactoryService in multirft-server-config.wsdd and add pertinent values for connectionUrl,dbUsername,password.

ant -Dogsa.root=<location of ogsa install> deployGar -- This step deploys multi file RFT service in the service container 

Client :

There is command line client in the distribution.To run the client 

source setenv.sh or source setenv.csh

java org.globus.ogsa.gui.RFTClient  http://127.0.0.1:8080/ogsa/services/base/rft/MultiFileRFTFactoryService etc/transfer.xfr

provided you have container running at 8080 on 127.0.0.1 and edited etc/transfer.xfr to have valid source and destination urls.This client starts transferring 2 files at a time.


